wolf (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial Debian packaging scaffold (Phase 5.9-a).
  * Four binary packages: wolf-database, wolf-server, wolf-dashboard,
    and a `wolf` meta-package that depends on all three for the
    common all-in-one installation case.
  * Per-component venv build + Next.js standalone build land in
    slices 5.9-b/c/d.

